properties.headline: SCHEDULED ROADWORK Bridge Installation - NORTH RYDE Delhi Road between Julius Avenue AND Epping Road
properties.otherAdvice:
Delhi Rd is closed on Saturday night until Sunday afternoon to facilitate the third of four installation stages of the Lachlan's Line pedestrian and cycle bridge. Access will be maintained to homes, businesses, public spaces and North Ryde Metro Station from the north via Fullers Rd and Pacific Highway.

Additionally:

  • Fri 21 Feb 8pm to Mon 24 Feb 5am: the M2 westbound on-ramp from Delhi Rd will be closed (motorists should use the Herring Rd on-ramp to access the M2). One eastbound lane on Delhi Rd will also be closed at Epping Rd
  • Sat 22 Feb 7pm to Sun 23 Feb 1pm: the M2 eastbound off-ramp to Delhi Rd will be left turn only from (motorists should use the Lane Cove Rd exit to access Epping Rd)

There will be delays around Delhi Rd and the M2 as well as additional traffic on diversion routes. Motorists should plan ahead, allow additional travel time, follow directions from signs and traffic controllers, and avoid the area if possible.

properties.headline: SCHEDULED ROADWORK - NORTH RYDE Delhi Rd westbound on-ramp to M2 Motorway
properties.otherAdvice:

While the ramp is closed, one eastbound lane of Delhi Rd will also be closed from Epping Rd.

Additionally:

  • Sat 22 Feb 8pm to Sun 23 Feb 1pm: Delhi Rd will be closed between Julius Ave and Epping Rd (motorists should use Epping Rd or Lane Cove Rd & Pacific Hwy as an alternative)
  • Sat 22 Feb 7pm to Sun 23 Feb 1pm: the M2 eastbound off-ramp to Delhi Rd will be left turn only (motorists should use the Lane Cove Rd exit to access Epping Rd)

There will be delays around Delhi Rd and the M2 as well as additional traffic on diversion routes. Motorists should plan ahead, allow addition travel time, follow directions from signs and traffic controllers, and avoid the area if possible.
